<h4 id="orgb9f2ff3"><span class="section-number-4">1.1.1.</span> nmap</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-1-1-1">
<p>
As always start off with the nmap.
</p>

<div class="org-src-container">
<pre class="src src-sh">sudo nmap -A -oA scans/onlyForyou 10.129.62.243
</pre>
</div>

<p>
The nmap flag <code>-A</code> enables os detection, version detection and scripting + traceroute.
Flag <code>-oA</code> outputs in all formats.
</p>

