<h4 id="orgec80f49"><span class="section-number-4">1.1.3.</span> Finding subdomains with ffuf</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-1-1-3">
<p>
Thanks to the great work of IppSec, I learned a useful trick that will help me on future HTB boxes.<sup><a id="fnr.1" class="footref" href="#fn.1" role="doc-backlink">1</a></sup>
</p>

<p>
I had to filter out status code 301.
</p>
