<div id="outline-container-org135fc87" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org135fc87"><span class="section-number-3">1.3.</span> Foothold enumeration</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-3">
<p>
Now that I have a foothold, it's time to enumerate with LinPEAS.
</p>

<p>
I'll leave the exercise of uploading a tool to the target host as an exercise for the reader.<sup><a id="fnr.4" class="footref" href="#fn.4" role="doc-backlink">4</a></sup>  Once I got LinPEAS.sh onto the host, I started with some basic enumeration.
</p>

<p>
The following is a great example of why you should always run <code>netstat</code>:
</p>

<pre class="example" id="orgb0324f9">
tcp        0      0 127.0.0.1:8001          0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -
tcp        0      0 127.0.0.1:33060         0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -
tcp        0      0 127.0.0.1:3306          0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -
tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:80              0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      1040/nginx: worker
tcp        0      0 127.0.0.53:53           0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -
tcp        0      0 0.0.0.0:22              0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -
tcp        0      0 127.0.0.1:3000          0.0.0.0:*               LISTEN      -
